subtitles.original: Thank you so much for coming to watch the 3D Birthday Live!
subtitles.english: Thank you so much for coming to watch the 3D Birthday Live!

subtitles.original: How was it? Did you feel my love?
subtitles.english: How was it? Did you feel my love?

subtitles.original: Eh, look at that! It's the specially prepared bedroom. Cute, isn't it?
subtitles.english: Eh, look at that! It's the specially prepared bedroom. Cute, isn't it?

subtitles.original: It has a bed, a sofa, Udin... and I don't know if you noticed, but...
subtitles.english: It has a bed, a sofa, Udin... and I don't know if you noticed, but...

subtitles.original: ...there was a display photo of the people I cherish the most in there.
subtitles.english: ...there was a display photo of the people I cherish the most in there.

subtitles.original: Did you catch it?
subtitles.english: Did you catch it?

subtitles.original: I think the neon stage was really cool too!
subtitles.english: I think the neon stage was really cool too!

subtitles.original: You probably spotted a bunch of TVs sitting around.
subtitles.english: You probably spotted a bunch of TVs sitting around.

subtitles.original: And well, those are there to help me watch you from afar.
subtitles.english: And well, those are there to help me watch you from afar.

subtitles.original: Cool, right?
subtitles.english: Cool, right?

subtitles.original: Ah, but come to think of it, I really did drag you around the stages, huh?
subtitles.english: Ah, but come to think of it, I really did drag you around the stages, huh?

subtitles.original: Um, how are you? Do you feel sick? Are you okay?
subtitles.english: Um, how are you? Do you feel sick? Are you okay?

subtitles.original: Ollie was a bit worried, but I think it shouldn't affect you too much since I carried you while you were still sleeping...
subtitles.english: Ollie was a bit worried, but I think it shouldn't affect you too much since I carried you while you were still sleeping...

subtitles.original: Hah? What? No, nothing!
subtitles.english: Hah? What? No, nothing!

subtitles.original: I didn't say anything! Haha! Um...
subtitles.english: I didn't say anything! Haha! Um...

subtitles.original: Speaking of you, you kept running and hiding away from me.
subtitles.english: Speaking of you, you kept running and hiding away from me.

subtitles.original: Naughty, naughty! Tsk, tsk!
subtitles.english: Naughty, naughty! Tsk, tsk!

subtitles.original: You always leave comments and like every post I make, so I thought you'd like it if I came to visit.
subtitles.english: You always leave comments and like every post I make, so I thought you'd like it if I came to visit.

subtitles.original: I didn't think it would actually surprise you that much.
subtitles.english: I didn't think it would actually surprise you that much.

subtitles.original: I think maybe it was because you were too surprised when I suddenly appeared in front of you.
subtitles.english: I think maybe it was because you were too surprised when I suddenly appeared in front of you.

subtitles.original: Yeah, hmm.
subtitles.english: Yeah, hmm.

subtitles.original: But just so you know, I worked really hard just for you.
subtitles.english: But just so you know, I worked really hard just for you.

subtitles.original: Ollie practiced singing, I sang a lot, and changed my outfit so many times!
subtitles.english: Ollie practiced singing, I sang a lot, and changed my outfit so many times!

subtitles.original: And I wonder if my feelings reached you? Hehe.
subtitles.english: And I wonder if my feelings reached you? Hehe.

subtitles.original: But they obviously did, right?
subtitles.english: But they obviously did, right?

subtitles.original: Also, at the end, I finally managed to catch you.
subtitles.english: Also, at the end, I finally managed to catch you.

subtitles.original: That's what you hoped for, right?
subtitles.english: That's what you hoped for, right?

subtitles.original: I mean, because you were running away from me...
subtitles.english: I mean, because you were running away from me...

subtitles.original: ...because you love me a lot! Obviously you were expecting it too, right?
subtitles.english: ...because you love me a lot! Obviously you were expecting it too, right?

subtitles.original: Hehe... period!
subtitles.english: Hehe... period!

subtitles.original: Anyway, for those of you who are still watching, thank you by the way. I have an announcement!
subtitles.english: Anyway, for those of you who are still watching, thank you by the way. I have an announcement!

subtitles.original: Ollie will be featured in SO87's song "Love Me Back" with the music video!
subtitles.english: Ollie will be featured in SO87's song "Love Me Back" with the music video!

subtitles.original: It's going to be so cool, so keep an eye out, okay? Mm-hmm!
subtitles.english: It's going to be so cool, so keep an eye out, okay? Mm-hmm!

subtitles.original: Ah, it's just so exciting, isn't it?
subtitles.english: Ah, it's just so exciting, isn't it?

subtitles.original: If you ever feel the need to feel Ollie's love again, then don't hesitate and please come back to watch the 3D Birthday Live again, okay?
subtitles.english: If you ever feel the need to feel Ollie's love again, then don't hesitate and please come back to watch the 3D Birthday Live again, okay?

subtitles.original: Ollie will always be here, waiting for you. Hehe.
subtitles.english: Ollie will always be here, waiting for you. Hehe.

subtitles.original: Anyways, bye bye! Otsucrazy~!
subtitles.english: Anyways, bye bye! Otsucrazy~!
